(6, 1, '2015-02-16 05:21:30', '2015-02-16 05:21:30', '<h2>Welcome to <span class="red">RED</span> <span class="blue">Tuition</span></h2>\r\nWe are a <strong>live and interactive</strong> online tuition company covering the <strong>General and Advanced Mathematics HSC</strong>. We help by providing weekly tuition and also pre-exam seminar courses which are all accessed by logging in to our website which uses the <strong>latest online training technology</strong> – ‘gototraining’. Students learn by viewing presentations which are filmed <strong>live</strong> with the assistance of <strong>fully animated</strong> study aids, they can stop tutors and ask as many questions as they need. Students are even provided with the <strong>private phone numbers</strong> of their tutors for any after hours support. We provide an <strong>in depth, organised, effective and interactive</strong> form of tuition which won’t drain your back pockets. Please have a look at how we can help you by checking out our <a class="red-un" href="http://111.93.163.213/RedTution/php/weekly-tuition/">weekly tuition</a> and our <a class="red-un" href="http://111.93.163.213/RedTution/php/pre-exam-seminars/">pre exam seminar courses</a> and <a class="red-un" href="http://111.93.163.213/RedTution/php/pricing/">try us out for free</a> to see whether we are right for you.', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2015-04-08 23:45:50', '2015-04-08 23:45:50', '', 0, 'http://111.93.163.213/RedTution/php/?page_id=6', 0, 'page', '', 0),
