(346, 1, '2015-04-03 06:11:38', '2015-04-03 06:11:38', '<p  class="fnt-size"><strong>Quickly get yourself completely ready to tackle Trials and the HSC with our holistic pre exam seminars.</strong></p>\r\n<p class="video"><img src="http://111.93.163.213/RedTution/php/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/iStock_000031045570Large-.jpg" alt="iStock_000031045570Large-" width="4300" height="2714" /></p>\r\n<ul class="right-top">\r\n	<li><strong>Entire HSC syllabus - </strong>Brilliantly planned, structured and presented seminars which cover the entire HSC syllabus in depth. Each day will focus on a particular section of the syllabus and every single syllabus dot point will be taught and tested.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Live - </strong>Each day is filmed live and is accessed by students via webinar.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Interactive - </strong>There are interactive quizzes throughout the seminars.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Expert Teachers - </strong>Mitchell Zalai will be the head tutor for the pre exam seminars, boasting an ATAR of 98.85 Mitchell is a future doctor and also has five years of private tutoring experience. A further two tutors will be announced in the lead up to the event.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>7 days with 4 hours of seminars on each day - </strong>Totalling 28 hours of teaching. Start at 8am, finish by 1:30pm. Students are advised to complete one HSC past paper after each day, this enables them to be completely prepared in all aspects from theory into practice.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class="clear-div"></div>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Learn in the comfort of your own home - </strong>or anywhere else with internet!</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Free study notes</strong> to summarise the theory of the entire subject.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Inexpensive</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul class="no-dot" style="text-align:center;">\r\n	<li><a class="start-btn" style="color: #fff;" href="http://111.93.163.213/RedTution/php/seminar-timetables/" class="red-un">Click here Seminar Timetables</a></li>\r\